  "3250100": {
    "name": "Sunset Bite",
    "steam_appid": 3250100,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250100/extras/b583ec5f41702181d41f1729790f4157.poster.avif?t=1742571671\" width=594 height=74 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250100/extras/b583ec5f41702181d41f1729790f4157.webm?t=1742571671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a beautiful world above the clouds, you finally have a chance after having a tragic life, now living as a humble farmer. Your new responsibility is to nourish the souls with your food for those preparing to depart. Cultivate vibrant crops, forge connections with unique characters, and uncover the secrets of this ethereal world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you embrace your second chance?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250100/extras/2440fb0d2a6b535b7b8d446956fc53c0.poster.avif?t=1742571671\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250100/extras/2440fb0d2a6b535b7b8d446956fc53c0.webm?t=1742571671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250100/extras/2440fb0d2a6b535b7b8d446956fc53c0.mp4?t=1742571671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the changing seasons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250100/extras/4014eb974f1f99eae44f3cfb50d98ea5.poster.avif?t=1742571671\" width=594 height=74 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250100/extras/4014eb974f1f99eae44f3cfb50d98ea5.webm?t=1742571671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cooking isn’t just a side activity—it’s an essential part of your adventure. With over 100 unique dishes to prepare, players will need to gather ingredients through farming, foraging, and purchasing from various vendors. Each dish requires players to participate in fun, interactive cooking mini-games, where precision and timing are key to success.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250100/extras/e90c82b9edc2047873293b390d137381.poster.avif?t=1742571671\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250100/extras/e90c82b9edc2047873293b390d137381.webm?t=1742571671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250100/extras/e90c82b9edc2047873293b390d137381.mp4?t=1742571671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow over 50 different crops in different seasons. Plant fruit trees to get unlimited supply of your favorite fruits. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250100/extras/8a778a84d4dfedac0f191d32fe707661.poster.avif?t=1742571671\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250100/extras/8a778a84d4dfedac0f191d32fe707661.webm?t=1742571671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250100/extras/8a778a84d4dfedac0f191d32fe707661.mp4?t=1742571671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather materials, construct a wide range of structures, furniture and decorate your farm and house as your liking. <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250100/extras/742991e4ae0f0494682d69a7967a9819.poster.avif?t=1742571671\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250100/extras/742991e4ae0f0494682d69a7967a9819.webm?t=1742571671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fishing is relaxing yet rewarding with a big range of fishes to catch. You have to set traps in lakes, rivers, and oceans. Catch them all!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250100/extras/0fad4fbf335e406e18fb7dcb4793c7ec.poster.avif?t=1742571671\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250100/extras/0fad4fbf335e406e18fb7dcb4793c7ec.webm?t=1742571671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250100/extras/0fad4fbf335e406e18fb7dcb4793c7ec.mp4?t=1742571671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forage in the wild to gather a variety of natural resources like mushrooms, flowers, and more. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250100/extras/d40c4b7ca80a64edb97aa27876a4975f.poster.avif?t=1742571671\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250100/extras/d40c4b7ca80a64edb97aa27876a4975f.webm?t=1742571671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250100/extras/d40c4b7ca80a64edb97aa27876a4975f.mp4?t=1742571671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wander in deep mines to collect ores, to turn them into gems or upgrade your tools.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250100/extras/54203ae9969488a7d41d80d1b5b471b8.poster.avif?t=1742571671\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250100/extras/54203ae9969488a7d41d80d1b5b471b8.webm?t=1742571671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250100/extras/54203ae9969488a7d41d80d1b5b471b8.mp4?t=1742571671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make friends with 40 townsfolk and unlock there backstories. And make right decision to have a romantic relationship with one of the 10+ Marriage  candidates.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250100/extras/f43b0dc8f0ca2052192f911726f6b884.poster.avif?t=1742571671\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250100/extras/f43b0dc8f0ca2052192f911726f6b884.webm?t=1742571671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250100/extras/f43b0dc8f0ca2052192f911726f6b884.mp4?t=1742571671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
